{
  "text": "The ratios of the temperature dependence exponents for the air width coefficients vs. J max + 0.1 \u2044 (J max \u00c0 K max ) are plotted in Fig. 10 (b). As in Fig. 10 dependence exponents reported in Ref. [CITATION_1] . As in Fig. 10(a) uncertainties corresponding to the error codes for the HITRAN2012 values are not considered in the present plots.",
